Package: melonmundiShinyUI
Title: Shared Theme and UI Helpers for MelonMundi Shiny Apps
Version: 0.2.1
Authors@R: person(given = "MelonMundi", family = "Team", email = "contato@melonmundi.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Author: MelonMundi Team [aut, cre]
Maintainer: MelonMundi Team <contato@melonmundi.com>
Description: Centralizes the shared MelonMundi visual theme and reusable UI
    helper functions for internal Shiny applications. The package provides a
    stable CSS dependency plus composable helpers for cards, alerts, footer,
    inline actions, status lines, loading states and other recurring app
    surfaces.
